title: Tuesday Post Show (02-22-22)
itunes:title: Tuesday Post Show (02-22-22)
description:
Bobby starts with a story about how men will think they are smart at something with no real knowledge on the subject. He also shares how the show podcast will now be loaded up moving forward. Raymundo talks about going to Disney World over the weekend and shares his Top 5 things he learned. Raymundo also talks about how Amy disrespected him. We talked about more news we didn’t get to during the show. Amy also talks about finding a kid that she mentored over 10 years ago.
